        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &amp;quot;Scheme of awarding Eklavya Award, Sardar Patel Award and Jaidipsinhji Award&amp;quot; by the Sports, Youth, and Cultural Activities Department, Government of Gujarat aims to recognize and incentivize the outstanding achievements of sportspersons by providing financial rewards across senior and junior categories based on their performances at state, national, and international levels. The scheme is implemented by the Sports Authority of Gujarat.\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n   1. **Eklavya Senior Award:** ₹1,00,000/-.   1. **Eklavya Junior Award:** ₹50,000/-.   1. **Sardar Patel Senior Award**: ₹50,000/-.   1. **Sardar Patel Junior Award:** ₹25,000/-.   1. **Jaidipsinhji Senior Award:** ₹20,000/-.   1. **Jaidipsinhji Junior Award:** ₹10,000/-.\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme \"Scheme of awarding Eklavya Award, Sardar Patel Award and Jaidipsinhji Award\" aims to encourage sporting excellence by providing financial awards to sportspersons for their achievements at the state, national, and international levels.",
