          "process_md": "&lt;br&gt;\n\n> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the homepage of the [Sports Authority of Gujarat](https://sportsauthority.gujarat.gov.in/).\n**Step 2:** Click on the “Registration” button on the upper-right side of the page.\n**Step 3:** Fill in all the required details as per the form and submit it.\n> **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** After registration, check your registered email for login credentials.\n**Step 2:** Select “Player” as the user type and log in using the credentials received.\n**Step 3:** Click on the concerned scheme name and proceed with the application.\n<br>\n\n"
